data.description: Spring is here and the POOL is open! Beautiful walkout ranch home has soaring ceilings and is flooded with natural light. Fall in love with the stunning open floor plan. Spacious kitchen offers tons of cabinet and counter space, plus a large walk in pantry. 3 bedrooms and laundry on the main level. Finished basement has everything for the entire family including a 4th bedroom, 3/4 bath, large wet bar, and workout room/extra storage! If that's not impressive, journey outside to the MASSIVE sport pool in the fully fenced in yard. Here you can lounge on the cover deck or concrete patio all summer long!
